  "id": "api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler",
  "title": "animationFrameScheduler",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L50-L49\" aria-label=\"編輯建議\" title=\"編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts#L50-L49\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index\", \"name\": \"rxjs/index\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\", \"name\": \"animationFrameScheduler\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/index\">rxjs/index</a>\n    </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"animationframescheduler\">animationFrameScheduler<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#animationframescheduler\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">穩定</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-result=\"on\">動畫幀排程器</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Animation Frame Scheduler</p>\n\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a>: AnimationFrameScheduler;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\"><span class=\"informal\">在 <code>window.requestAnimationFrame</code> 觸發時執行任務</span></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><span class=\"informal\">Perform task when <code>window.requestAnimationFrame</code> would fire</span></p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrame\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrame</a></code> 排程器與延遲一起使用時，它將回退到 <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> 排程器行為。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When <code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrame\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrame</a></code> scheduler is used with delay, it will fall back to <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> scheduler\nbehaviour.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">無需延遲，<code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrame\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrame</a></code> 排程器可用於建立流暢的瀏覽器動畫。它能確保已安排的任務將在下一次瀏覽器內容重繪之前發生，從而儘可能高效地執行動畫。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Without delay, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrame\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrame</a></code> scheduler can be used to create smooth browser animations.\nIt makes sure scheduled task will happen just before next browser content repaint,\nthus performing animations as efficiently as possible.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"example\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">安排 div 高度動畫</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Schedule div height animation</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n// html: &#x3C;div style=\"background: #0ff;\">&#x3C;/div>\nimport { <a href=\"api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">animationFrameScheduler</a> } <a href=\"api/index/function/from\" class=\"code-anchor\">from</a> 'rxjs';\n\nconst div = document.querySelector('div');\n\nanimationFrameScheduler.schedule(function(height) {\n  div.style.height = height + \"px\";\n\n  this.schedule(height + 1);  // `this` references currently executing Action,\n                              // which we reschedule with new state\n}, 0, 0);\n\n// You will see a div element growing in height\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/deprecations\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/animationFrame\n - api/index/function/observeOn\n - api/operators/observeOn\n - guide/scheduler\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/animationFrame\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#animationframescheduler\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#description\n - api/index/const/animationFrameScheduler#example\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - api/index/function/from\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L50-L49\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/animationFrame.ts#L50-L49\n-->"
